title: Rules to Better Code and Successful Projects
sessionTitle: Rules to Better Code and Successful Projects
eventShortDescription: ​Managing a team of coders can be a tricky experience, especially as most coders like to do things their own way. During this session we go through a list of rules that help make the development process as smooth as possible. These rules govern the creation of specifications and schedules, best methods for testing and fixing bugs and even the employees working conditions.
